<subSubSection id="C31B655EFFD5FFA6FF35FC2EFCE3FC12" pageId="11" pageNumber="140" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="8BBE36D5FFD5FFA6FF35FC2EFCE3FC12" blockId="11.[136,1452,482,977]" pageId="11" pageNumber="140">
<emphasis id="B975EAC7FFD5FFA6FF35FC2EFE65FC6E" bold="true" box="[189,491,914,940]" pageId="11" pageNumber="140">Distribution and habitat</emphasis>
:―This subspecies is endemic to Antikithira and the northern part of Gramvousa promontory, west 
<collectingRegion id="49C5F837FFD5FFA6FEDBFC0AFE05FC12" box="[339,395,950,976]" country="Greece" name="Kriti" pageId="11" pageNumber="140">Kriti</collectingRegion>
, where it grows mostly on coastal habitats.
</paragraph>
